data.description: Take a look at this one! This beautiful like-new Bloomfield home is a dream come true in the wonderful Godley Ranch community of Godley.  Highlights of the neighborhood include simple and seamless access to Godley ISD schools and other city amenities surrounded by a rural and picturesque landscape. The custom and ornate front door invites you into the grand entryway with charm and style.  You're greeted by the open-concept kitchen and living area with plenty of room for entertaining.  Tasteful quartz countertops, custom and warm-colored cabinetry, and a large kitchen island highlight the kitchen space.  The living room is both large and cozy, the perfect mix.  Spacious bedrooms which offer flex space for multiple offices and-or dining areas.  The primary bedroom is spacious with well-maintained finishes and adjoined with a large walk-in closet and a spa-like primary bathroom.  The upstairs space could be used as a theater-game room, or second living area.  Come see this one soon!!
